{"tid":832972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★攞飛混亂逾百人櫃位排長龍　乘客：以後唔搭高鐵","createTime":"2018-09-23T07:10:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T09:02:04.000Z","uid":19454,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7547b7472aaeb403bcbcdf76939a54cf33d3ab35","tid":832972,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T07:10:37.000Z","msg":"廣深港高鐵香港段今(23日)首日開通，但不少在網上購票的旅客都無法在西九龍站內的自助取票機取票，需要排隊到櫃台取票。下午約2時有逾百人排隊等候取票，有市民直斥安排混亂，更表示<span style=\"color: red;\">日後不會再在香港搭高鐵</span>。<br />\n<br />\n現場所見，西九龍站雖設有約20部自助購票及取票機，未見有排隊人龍。港鐵貼出告示，指示透過內地鐵總網站「12306」購票的旅客，需到1至5號櫃位人手取票。記者上前向港鐵職員查問，職員表示自助取票機只供透過香港網站購票的乘客取票。<br />\n<br />\n市民方先生原本透過12306網站訂購了後日(25日)到佛山西的車票，他趁今日有空在早上10時許特地來西九龍站取票，惟見人龍太長，在近下午1時才開始排隊，但排了約1個小時仍未排到，「攞飛咁麻煩，我搭咁多高鐵都未試過咁，香港呢個高鐵站真係最失敗！廣州南呢啲大站都唔會排咁耐啦。」他又指，港鐵職員只向他表示因網絡問題，因此排隊需時。方揚言，對西九龍站安排非常失望，以後不會再由香港乘搭高鐵，寧願坐車到福田再轉乘。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180923/bkn-20180923142718564-0923_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180923%2Fbkn-20180923142718564-0923_00822_001.html&d=vTi2tvMzgm8sWSCP0n%2FUb0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=961ed1c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180923/bkn-20180923142718564-0923_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"6b0015f1cb9a646a1b9e0cc222754727bdafe397","tid":832972,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T07:10:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e69d815221e3c3110ee9f81372d52a0e1872a47f","tid":832972,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T07:14:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 低鐵"},{"pid":"7281f77f7bc30cbd1275e74951a8c68d8aaabd57","tid":832972,"uid":54337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T07:19:29.000Z","msg":"唔搭高鐵，係咪想搞港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d3661613d48946c1ed261cafcdf21cb2bfe3886","tid":832972,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T07:21:15.000Z","msg":"部機一向任意唔出飛比香港人"},{"pid":"e62301a04e446b53cbecef0a7f8401e9816c2fed","tid":832972,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d3661613d48946c1ed261cafcdf21cb2bfe3886","tid":832972,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T07:21:15.000Z","msg":"部機一向任意唔出飛比香港人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T07:23:52.000Z","msg":"低端人口"},{"pid":"b663b96b9784f01c5b351a7ded87231280f1fc4d","tid":832972,"uid":103325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T07:24:58.000Z","msg":"更表示日後不會再在香港搭高鐵。<br />\n<br />\n漢奸，唔愛黨愛國<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf993c3cd4652aaf9a5307717979e30037931fe4","tid":832972,"uid":146604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T07:27:04.000Z","msg":"俾長城block左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4eb4aa75729984b666cf467cd7bcc88c851a5b3","tid":832972,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T07:31:02.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好再搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00854d322cd1fcc42424d359ac4863bd0b7e474d","tid":832972,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T08:30:22.000Z","msg":"逼你用mtr嗰網買？"},{"pid":"e1cc40ca1a72c01dfc5eae4cb6ed15dd982a48da","tid":832972,"uid":165012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T08:53:28.000Z","msg":"再嘈叫公安過黎拉鳩你<br />\n過一過黎話咁易"},{"pid":"607d268a5167f555e36578037cc79635ba6fa555","tid":832972,